CHZZK
=====

This project is a personal fork/rework of the MIT-licensed upstream project:

- Upstream: bass9030/FUCK-CHZZK-GRID
- Upstream purpose: browser extension for CHZZK high-quality playback behavior
- Upstream license: MIT

The upstream MIT license text is preserved in LICENSE. Local changes rename the project to CHZZK and add
project-specific validation, testing, documentation, and safer diagnostics.
